Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.99,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Love，I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.26,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.65,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.70,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh，you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:13.29,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:15.53,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:19.32,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:26.55,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:30.03,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:37.96,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:43.72,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:47.25,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Calling you，so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:50.67,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:53.81,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wish I could see your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.88,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}My love，you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.37,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:03.84,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:11.25,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Oh，you are the one I believe
