Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（公共电话）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  火村学长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕一秒  我也不想让你再待在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自说自话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一个没有那家伙的地方  让我们重新开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真强硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  既然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  久濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醒过来就看见你们  我还是下地狱的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打119吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,000就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  不用叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才  我把和瑞希的关系了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此分手  相信今后不会再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像与前女友那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不激扬青春吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就不是谈青春的年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想了结我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果做过火的话  连回忆都会消失得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没有不舍得忘掉的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总还是有点快乐的经历吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经走得很远啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下面该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没计划过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去填饱肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先逛逛房产中介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个住处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  不想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说不吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没理由要硬撑着不吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想出人头地了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我而抛弃人生  可不会有什么好处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做…你早晚会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经后悔过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会再后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过吧  我是你的初恋情人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说过  初恋还持续着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.28,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  叨扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.17,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来啊…好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  平时都是立即回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我喜欢你  这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这一点一直都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是谎言  是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍着不眨眼  可真够累人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.24,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连身份都说不清  谁会租房给我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说得还不够清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是离家出走的学生两名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份可疑的两人这一点是够清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼…找不到房子  今晚睡哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地缺乏计划性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种突发状况下  怎么定计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚就找个旅馆住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀学长  你刚才往不健康的方向想了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁  谁想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说傻话也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个…可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去旅馆住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找到工作前  储蓄必须得省着花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可住处要是定不下来  工作也无从谈起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是基督徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不都是神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您今晚赐我们容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏是夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是冬天就冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的夜晚也很凉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样一来就暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不是纯洁之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是优子这一点没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你变成什么样  我的心意也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始建20年前  四叠半的单间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.69,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：叠是日本特有面积单位，大小在1.6平方米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房卫生间一律共用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种条件  房租居然还比我之前租的地方贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押金礼金全免  立刻可以入住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠那种应付差事的身份证明就能租房给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专供有难言之隐人士的公寓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须得注意防盗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连手机都没有的人  还有什么东西怕被盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节时买给她的红色手表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…你去世妹妹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯独没法丢弃它…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  写生簿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用它来打发时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是你扔给我的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…因为这个你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在同情我  在可怜我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想要那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是因为那样才跟你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻…居然相信了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  你也只是把我当作自我满足的道具不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感受  对你来说都无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和明良兄长有什么区别！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  也许你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和雨宫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在为没能保护好茜而懊悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这不是同情  也不是什么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是用你做茜的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  我只是想保护你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会松开这双手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:31.74,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}从天空中摇曳着飘落下一根白色羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦  夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是实习  没正式工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭做好了  快趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说  再怎么寒酸的公寓里也得有电灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人住的时候  可没有过回到家里有灯亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家时有人在等着的感觉真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是回来晚了我就关灯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门锁了睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哭着求情也不给你开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一定要早点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君回家的地方  也是我回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  这里也是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个累赘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君至今的所有努力都付之流水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我画像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长人物画…不过还是画画看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说和前女友分手的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她反倒替我哭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我都没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么…现在的我特别想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有经历过挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是因为我不会去做可能失败的事而选择逃避罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把我扔进这个无法逃避的游戏里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要让我去玩一场注定会输的游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心脏…还有瑞希…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我这个没有未来的人还能做什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底我还能再做些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  我明白你的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在崩溃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的你们又能明白什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算你自暴自弃  也不会有什么好结果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都死到临头了  还会有什么好结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就放弃的话  你什么也得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-40,0:00:00.-40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想听你教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂得死心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了地继续着已经结束的游戏的家伙又懂得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不会再见到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不会再见到…雨宫优子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣的钱够糊口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可中途退学的你很难找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来买包烟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想让我把优子交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  也不是我能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道优子会想回你那里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若没有别的地方可回的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也只能这样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是没法做她的归宿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是她的避难所  并不是真的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问原因  那是因为你自己也一直在逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没逃吗  那个地震的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  你把唯一的妹妹给丢弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起  你就远离争斗  只是不断逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才会放开优子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又放弃了画画  放弃了颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着我  逃避着曾经的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  你只是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说我还能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你自己也意识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不小心了  买个像样点的锁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正能做的  就是在那场地震中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你妹妹一起死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一清二楚的  要问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也曾想过要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那一天我却没有在妹妹身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是十分羡慕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时  又十分地恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  你和你妹妹是在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有去救你妹妹  而是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有去和你妹妹一起死掉  而是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.39,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明明是你重要的妹妹  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在恐惧和痛苦中呼唤着你  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以和她一起去死  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明明是衷心期盼的命运  而你却逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为她赎罪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你获得她的宽恕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能坦然地去寻找幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  你还会再一次失去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的归宿都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要…失去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在逃吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…又在逃了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君  夕君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕君  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来吧  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  火村学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪学长  你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想青春一把吗  这下满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「明明不会再见到雨宫优子了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不说出这句话  我死都不能瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕  倒是你才不要老纠结着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久濑  你知道有些话能说  有些话不能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  说来凪也还纠结着那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好冷静一下头脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  你会存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都有段时间没做过梦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希  有你的东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是久濑先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送货的人搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  住址写的是这里  收件人也是瑞希哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-40,0:00:00.-40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正坏掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:53.68,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是久濑先生吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让海风弄潮小提琴可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候真的很受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪姐居然说自己是女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算硬让两人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心灵依旧相通  就没办法了结关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了结…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的时候  如果自己坠入情网就算输了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要让对方爱上自己才行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是久濑的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然充满久濑先生的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是被你爱上了  可就要输了的却是久濑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事…输到体无完肤的是我才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…好想哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:22:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙从来只打必胜之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他赢不了输了还能再站起来的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够拯救那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料外的邂逅  让心支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ef - a tale of melodies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,return
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗？  ——那真实的旋律
